7b4fb78e1722212d31418e2fd72b2023339cebf9041f0071eac4df2cd7364218b338b703247a8246f5b781c28640a2b9a569f83f9c920fa5a9de64616e7b9edf  0001-build-make-soname-explicit-and-simplify-and-fix-sona.patch"
